15 WHEREAS, this remarkable organization provides its members with access to valuable
16 educational and training resources, networking and communication support, and breaking
17 industry news and updates; and
18 WHEREAS, it is abundantly fitting and proper that the Georgia Airports Association be
19 appropriately honored.
20 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE SENATE that the members of this body
21 recognize February 27, 2025, as Georgia Airports Association Day.
22 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Secretary of the Senate is authorized and directed
23 to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the Georgia
24 Airports Association.
